analyst_base_prompt.content:
Analyze {analyse_type} {id} for {task_type}. Use these commands (max {max_step} steps):
(1) UserInfo[id] - get user information
(2) ItemInfo[id] - get item information  
(3) UserHistory[id,k] - get user's k interactions
(4) ItemHistory[id,k] - get item's k interactions
(5) Finish[result] - complete analysis

RULES: NO duplicates, gather 3-5 data points, then Finish.

Examples: {examples}
{fewshot}

Target: {analyse_type} {id}
{history}{hint}
